lead_paragraph: Brazil's President Michel Temer expressed on Tuesday his grief for the victims of a plane crash in Colombia that killed 76 people, including members of Brazilian soccer team Chapecoense and several journalists.

headline.print_headline: Brazil's Temer Voices Solidarity With Victims of Colombia Crash
